hard Sauder, Robert Seidel und die Herausgeber.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aEnlightenmentzGermanyvCongresses. 4aDer Teutsche Merkur (Zeitschr.). 4aMerck, Johann Heinrich. 4aWieland, Christoph M. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / German.2bisacsh1 aFECHNER, JÖRG-ULRICH, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFEDERHOFER, MARIE-THERES, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHEINZ, ANDREA, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLEUSCHNER, ULRIKE, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLUSERKE-JAQUI, MATTHIAS, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLeuschner, Ulrike, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aLuserke-Jaqui, Matthias, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aROSSBACH, NIKOLA, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSAUDER, GERHARD, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSEIDEL, ROBERT, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVOLLMER, HARTMUT, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Literary and Cultural Studies 2000 - 2014z9783110637854oZDB-23-GLC0 cprintz978311017571440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311090700140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110907001423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110907001/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GLCc2000d2014